&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coach managers through performance management, employee development, feedback, and complex employee relations matters.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Guide leaders through performance improvement plans, promotions, and talent calibration.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design, evolve, and run the semiannual performance review process, ensuring fairness and consistency across the company.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help managers build inclusive, high-performing teams through effective coaching and leadership practices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
